Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}1924年 圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被死神碰了 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说到底谁更可怕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所学校每到圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会变装地来 你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿普丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学你也换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说 我也没衣服可以换啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说 刚才塞西尔老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲 还没好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这不就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我在学校的圣诞派对上穿过的衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我虽然不过是个新来的帮佣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但塞西尔一定要两个人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想跟你一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿的…就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是玩偶服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏是用水晶珠子做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看吧 漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说血管都在闪闪发亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个莫非就是美兽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是流传在我国的一个传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怪谈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是个童话故事更确切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很浪漫的故事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本国 有一只化身为少女的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到一只兔子一直为她打杂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子武艺超群 打跑了所有想得到怪物而接近她的恶人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子就这么猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物也会劫富济贫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而代理她施舍的就是兔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物日渐受到人民的欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而当权者也将得到她作为权力的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而日益加紧行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当权者们终于杀死了想要保护怪物的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想 这样一来就能得到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物也已经不在世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那只兔子就是怪物的心脏 是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物和兔子实际上是一心同体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得心脏做得这么华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件衣服给久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你给维多利嘉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们翘首以待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我忘记阿普丽尔同学也喜欢久城同学了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想做美兽二代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我已经换好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短发妖精好可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是今天的变装皇后了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:38.52,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,570)}窗边圣歌缀薄幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小甜饼马上要跑出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉…你是不是甜食吃太多胖了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区食草哺乳动物还敢嚣张？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无边蕾丝飘飘下～～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是美兽传奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这裙子真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许摸我头！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你啊 你为啥想到这个点子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉的生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神一变成兔子也就没那么可怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会去跳舞吧 死神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来为大家所畏惧的黑色死神也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色妖精也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那么大家所有人的圣诞礼物已经装在这棵树上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家各取所需吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学 我们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选哪个好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选这个就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样做真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你妈妈考迪利亚女士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然把这么贵重的东西随便给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不知道会被谁拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你是随春而来的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我是兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正无论如何 你这个人肯定会让大家先选礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大众都盯着那些包装精美内容丰富的去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下那些不起眼的小礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上黑白蕾丝会让你联想起某人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你必然会选这个盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 一切都是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会珍惜的 我会一直把它当传家宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 我也有礼物要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等我一下 我给你拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我 我马上拿给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 虽然我懂是懂 但总还是不开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是金色妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是短发妖精啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是金发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为啥大家就不那么叫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 我染发去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要染成大红大绿的圣诞色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊饰跟戒指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么觉得我们想到一块去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请问你是久城一弥同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是鲁伯特国王陛下的手谕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿普丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个…给维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 阿普丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经采取措施 让他国的商人和官员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及留学生先行回国了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧洲终于也要燃起久违的战火了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 我国一贯以永久中立为政策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使世界发生巨变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国也应坚守本分 不被这股浪潮吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕就委任你了 罗杰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 正因为是乱世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街头巷尾最近传言甚多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所谓的传言是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣略有耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据称美兽再临我国了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,26
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,27
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 这太野蛮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么事先没有通知…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心 我们会将你平安送回国内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢陛下的好意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果战争爆发 那我们就无法送你回国了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后数年内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将有一狂风暴雨席卷世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们尚且身轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或会因这风暴而分离吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只兔子是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我们检查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的指示 我们奉的是国王陛下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想就这样分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抓住那个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话待会说 中国人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群潜伏在地下的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部给我抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨蹭了 趁现在快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么又碰上这种麻烦 你这人真令人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里 路易吉你不是和贾可琳小姐一起出城了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 多亏了她我才成了有钱人家的养子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直待在深宅大院里多拘谨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我偶尔跑出来重温以前的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这种生活也快到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟外面阿兵哥那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争快爆发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到刚才那些兔头队伍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队现在在镇压国内的危险分子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险分子是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于忧国忧民 拯救彷徨的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美兽据说会再次降临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美兽嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些兔头的口号就是「美兽所求即不义人之血」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说那些人是渴望打仗的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 组织不断扩大中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有传闻说他们想对现在软弱的政府实行行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些怕人的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去维多利嘉那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得很不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要拆散你们这一对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让一弥可以留在维多利嘉的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拜托格雷维尔看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但警部他是灵异部的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 他每次到紧要关头都会挺身而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次肯定也能帮上你们的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布罗瓦警部就算那样 看上去也是很担心维多利嘉…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨义德跟伊梅尔达也走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回宿舍去吧 维多利嘉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是把这身衣服换了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这吊坠真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学还真懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿点吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请苏菲小姐做些热汤来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这个吊坠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随时随地都会去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论何时都在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说大话了 久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在明明…这么想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说让他逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让他落入了灵异部之手的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是落到我们手里又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老蜥蜴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…该叫美兽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵异部用人之时终于也到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让那些人利用我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不妨就在这里自我了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做傻事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对将要震撼世界的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的存亡不如一叶孤舟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我存在 那这个国家的平衡就会受到影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数人将要流血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将诞生无数被迫母子分离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饱尝人间孤苦的可怜人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样 我还不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能看到我吗 可能看不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 有一只兔子误入网中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为美兽会无条件地服从我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就利用那只兔子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个傻松鼠 不 傻兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没意识到他已经成为人质了 只是想要见到你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你敢对他下手…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全部取决于你的回复了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和维多利嘉果然不会就这样分开的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布罗瓦警部还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能先进去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点见到维多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 我会助你们一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此相对 不准任何人碰他一根手指头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是妹妹的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我还是要听的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子是美兽的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子一死 美兽自然就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个不会就此分开的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 把我现在想要的东西给我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.31,0:24:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是甜点 也不是谜案
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想要温暖的无聊时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.41,0:24:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 快给我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:30.10,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,547)}蒙灰棋局喝将死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【STAFF】
